Description: COMET provides an open source simulation to model the United States lung allocation process within synthetic candidate and donor populations. For additional functionality, this package interacts with data that is available in the 'cometdata' package. To access this data run "remotes::install_github('https://github.com/ClevelandClinicQHS/cometdata', type = 'source')".
